2. Create a new IAM policy named "Udacity-temp" with the following policy

```
{
    "Version": "2012-10-17",
    "Statement": [
        {
            "Effect": "Allow",
            "Action": [
                "ec2:DescribeInstances"
            ],
            "Resource": "*"
        }
    ]
}
```

3. Observe that the Region selector doesn't let you change to another region because IAM is "global."
